section     Dropbox

echo        Don't allow notifications for Dropbox when first syncing,
echo        it will constantly update you with "Files added" popups.
echo
echo        Dropbox will ask for permission to control your Mac two ways:
echo        1. Accessibility access via System Preferences.
echo        2. Repeated prompts for your password to gain admin access.
echo
alert       Do not allow either, it will sync files just fine without.

remind      Turn on Dropbox notifications once sync has finished.

brewfile

start       Dropbox
alert       Get Dropbox syncing files before continuing.
